{"tid":2077784,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「白屋」擬重設　無限期扣押拷問政治犯","createTime":"2020-06-24T14:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T14:41:52.000Z","uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"24dc7a7451132389c00e05cbb6339b52e80a9756","tid":2077784,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T14:07:45.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】港版國安法最快本月底在人大完成審議並通過，但條文細節仍然未公佈，港人的人權保障堪憂。有報道指港府將就港版國安法，設立港英時代惡名昭彰的「白屋」政治犯扣押中心，可以將疑犯無限期拘留。特首林鄭月娥昨晨出席行政會議前見記者，聲稱由於港版國安法的草案說明未有任何相關內容，「所以我不能評論」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>涂謹申憂酷刑逼供</strong>（一早有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n《南華早報》報道，當局擬設置特定的扣留中心，盤問調查涉及國安案件的疑犯，而不會在警署內審問疑犯，用途類似殖民地年代位於摩星嶺的白屋。報道沒有提及擬設扣留中心的地點，惟引述多個消息稱，新扣留設施未知是由香港警方管理抑或由中央駐港國安公署負責，由於國安案件與一般案件不同，疑犯被扣查的時間可能長於48小時，正式檢控及庭審前，疑犯或要一直被扣留。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200624/2OWBY3QUOIG6HH5FNMMZI3YNMQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2F2OWBY3QUOIG6HH5FNMMZI3YNMQ%2F&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPsyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=5efdeaaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2F2OWBY3QUOIG6HH5FNMMZI3YNMQ%2F&h=3c818b1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200624/2OWBY3QUOIG6HH5FNMMZI3YNMQ/</a>"},{"pid":"ca8be31f66fcc83a976caab2670aea99c87dc39c","tid":2077784,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T14:08:39.000Z","msg":"支持加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f7f3e54a3c735fa5b82a76bcc5b09e10a34c20","tid":2077784,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T14:12:43.000Z","msg":"可以將疑犯無限期拘留<br />\n<br />\n即係被自殺？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81ab8834abf43a168ecfa656430c671b14feb88"